IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents.advertisement

Class EmptyAdvertisementScheme

  • java.lang.Object
    • IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents.advertisement.AdvertisementScheme
      • IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents.advertisement.EmptyAdvertisementScheme

  • public class EmptyAdvertisementScheme
extends AdvertisementScheme
    Since in most models analyzed for deriving the specifications for IRPact the company agent is entirely passive (or non-existent), the DefaultAdvertisementScheme is a AdvertisementScheme in which the company agent doesn't act (i.e. has an empty advertiseProductPortfolio method). It serves to provide an implementation of a AdvertisementScheme so that instantiation of a CompanyAgent is possible
